### ============================================================================
### LLM-TOOL-API-001 | Grep 기반 코드 키워드 검색
### Markdown source: docs/03_Specifications/03_LLM/api/LLM_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: POST /api/search/{repo_id}/grep
### 관련 기능 ID: LLM-TOOL-B-205
### 상태: 시작 전
### ⚠️ DEPRECATED: 이 엔드포인트는 외부 공개 API가 아닙니다.
###               grep 기능은 LangGraph 내부 grep_worker tool contract로 이동되었습니다.
###               (ref: LLM_API_SPEC.md > 폐기된 이전 API, 2026-06-25 확인)
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e

### [정상] 문자열 검색
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/search/{{repoId}}/grep
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"pattern":"def embed_code","isRegex":false,"fileExtensions":[".py"],"maxResults":10}

### 200 OK
### {"code":200,"message":"success","data":{"pattern":"def embed_code","totalMatches":1,"results":[{"filePath":"backend/app/embed/service.py","lineNumber":12,"lineContent":"def embed_code(...):","context":"..."}]}}
### maxResults: Integer, 선택, 기본 20
### context: 매칭 줄 앞뒤 3줄

### [오류] 잘못된 정규식
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/search/{{repoId}}/grep
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"pattern":"[unclosed","isRegex":true,"maxResults":20}

### 400 INVALID_PATTERN / 401 UNAUTHORIZED / 404 REPO_NOT_FOUND / 500 GREP_FAILED
### {"code":400,"message":"정규식 패턴이 올바르지 않습니다.","data":null,"error":{"code":"INVALID_PATTERN","detail":"unclosed character class","field":"pattern","retryable":false}}
